    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >说明：抢先体验版本仅支持英文，中文版游戏将在完整版中推出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/900400/extras/7e66441100363de6743a16455a4ab612.avif?t=1759482280\" width=600 height=268 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/900400/extras/284be206083e140f8366d9f9b9c08e3f.webp?t=1759482280\" width=616 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗马人全副武装地踏过了哈德良长城。你唯一的希望就是抵达权力的中心 — 杜纳德，并团结起各支部族。但你首先要去警告忠厚的兄长维德，他是你在世上唯一的亲人，与此同时，父亲造成的痛苦仍然纠缠着你，而关于母亲的温暖回忆正在战火中渐渐消散。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会挽救那些与自己亲近的人，还是会不惜一切代价让帝国血债血偿？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/900400/extras/99c63ab041577f9912a39f4b26328292.poster.avif?t=1759482280\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/900400/extras/99c63ab041577f9912a39f4b26328292.webm?t=1759482280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/900400/extras/99c63ab041577f9912a39f4b26328292.mp4?t=1759482280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以自由定制角色的外观与特征，而这只是旅程的开始。在整个故事中，你可以选择自己的想法、言语和行动，进一步塑造你的身心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是否正在战斗，你的情绪都会影响掷骰的成功率。运用角色的意志力，在战斗中发挥出最佳水准，在谈判中获得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭露那些阻碍自己脚步的想法，将自己的心智铸成利刃，足以坚强地面对野兽、其他人以及自己的内心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/900400/extras/f119e45c7f6f196c81c47b72fd1c2822.poster.avif?t=1759482280\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/900400/extras/f119e45c7f6f196c81c47b72fd1c2822.webm?t=1759482280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/900400/extras/f119e45c7f6f196c81c47b72fd1c2822.mp4?t=1759482280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与栩栩如生的角色展开互动，洞悉他们的行事动机。作出影响人际关系的决定，与他们成为不共戴天的敌人或是甘愿赴汤蹈火的挚友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剖析你的对手，驾驭致命的战斗。宽恕、拯救、杀戮或是抛弃其他角色。你可以谨慎行事，也可以创造传奇般的壮举，角逐地位与权力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会选择侥幸求生，还是寻找值得为之奋斗的目标？你的抉择能否改变自己的命运，谱写一段流传千古的佳话？ </p>",
